des: Yesterday's Country is the station for lovers of Country Music...and we mean ALL of it. We play the entire history of Country Music, which is why we say The History of Country Music Lives here. Your 24 hour a day home for everything from Jimmie Rodgers to Kenny Rogers, from Kitty Wells to Faith Hill and everything in between. Give us a listen, we believe you'll want to stay awhile.
